parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or jerks while accelerating
has difficulty shifting gears
loses power
or is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, slip, or jerk while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch slips while driving
or the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: AYC/ACD pump failure can cause the all-wheel drive system to malfunction, leading to loss of traction and control, especially in slippery conditions.
symptoms: The all-wheel drive system fails to engage
the vehicle loses traction
or the AYC/ACD pump fails to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: CVT transmission overheating can cause the transmission to fail, leading to loss of power, hesitation, or jerking while driving.
symptoms: The transmission overheats
especially during high-speed driving
and may require frequent fluid changes or aftermarket transmission coolers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling and jerking issues can cause accidents, especially when driving on the highway, and can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when accelerating
jerks when accelerating
and may stall out completely
even on the highway.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system failure can cause the vehicle to shut off, resulting in loss of power and potentially leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle makes a clicking noise
dashboard lights flicker
and the vehicle may shut off completely
especially when in park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Bluetooth connectivity issues can cause distraction while driving, leading to accidents, and can disrupt important business or personal calls.
symptoms: The Bluetooth connection drops and reconnects frequently
causing calls to be lost or disrupted.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The dim headlights can reduce visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night. The charging issue can cause the area around the radio and cigarette lighter to become hot.
symptoms: The headlights are dim
making it difficult to see at night
and the area around the radio and cigarette lighter becomes hot when charging a cellular phone.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle's occupants are not protected from the impact.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact
resulting in injuries or fatalities.
